c: 33
v: 49
t: "Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ni mwubakane n’abakenyezi bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri hanyuma ni mwahukana nabo batambukanyi banyu imbere yuguhuza nabo ibitsina, ntavyicaro bafise muzoba harurirako, mugabo nimubahe ico mwoba shumbusha kandi muze mwahukane nabo munzira nziza z’amahoro"